data.description: Oversized brick ranch with 3 living spaces; living room, family room, and all season room. Walk in and see yourself in this home! Blonde hardwood floors are said to be throughout the original portion of the home even underneath the carpets in the bedrooms. This home is one floor living, with a step down into the family room that hosts the all brick gas log fireplace. Open kitchen and dining room area that is in between the living and family room. Seller favorite is the all seasons room off of the back of the home with the vaulted ceilings and wooden beam across the peak, it has nearly 180º of windows to allow ample natural light, built-ins, double mirrored closets with built-ins as well. The half wrap deck can be accessed from the all seasons room and the family room which is enclosed along with the back yard by a chain link fence on a level lot. There's gate entry to the front yard and drive way and also one to the alley way. Centrally located in north Parkersburg, set up your showing today!
